Class CompoundTermTag

java.lang.Object
  gnu.prolog.term.CompoundTermTag
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public final class CompoundTermTag
extends Object
implements Serializable

A tag of compound term such as foo/2. A tag consists of functor and arity. All tags are unique in one JVM.

Version:
0.0.1
Author:
Constatine Plotinikov
